    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "It does not seem a great problem because funds always move to the legit owner, however allowing everyone to trigger such a transfer is against the security principle of least authority. Think of a use case where the holdings grant some dividends as long as they are locked in the contract. What if the user prefers to keep holding after the timelock expires? With the current implementation the user doesn't have this option. ",
